snippet.title: Rising Empires 2 (Surface promo)
snippet.description: This is the first video of my hobby project Rising Empires 2. RE2 is an android strategy game that can be downloaded at the Google Play store. The world consists of two levels; the Surface and the Netherworld. The game play in this video show the Surface map.
